          "question": "<p><a name=\"5063\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>If&nbsp;\\( (a^{2}+b^{2}),(b^{2}+c^{2}) \\) and&nbsp;\\( (a^{2}+c^{2}) \\) are in geometric progression, which of the following holds true?</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>Quantitative Aptitude: CAT 2012 | Question: 8</b></p>",
